  "title": "CLASS 4 DELIVERY DRIVER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Efficiently handle daily islandwide delivery and collection tasks.</li>\n  <li>Load, unload, transport, and deliver cargo/goods, ensuring proper handling and secure placement.</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely and accurate delivery of goods/cargo to all destinations.</li>\n  <li>Conduct regular vehicle maintenance checks and ensure the vehicle is in good working condition.</li>\n  <li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned by the supervisor.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess a valid Singapore Class 4 driving license.</li>\n  <li>Physically fit and capable of lifting heavy cargo (up to 25kg).</li>\n  <li>Familiar with Singapore roads and committed to adhering to traffic rules and regulations.</li>\n  <li>Demonstrate responsibility and effective time management skills.</li>\n  <li>Willing to work overtime when required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>5.5-Day Work Week:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Monday to Friday:</strong> 8:30 am - 5:30 pm</li>\n  <li><strong>Saturday:</strong> 8:30 am - 12:30 pm</li>\n</ul>",
